WEBVTT

00:01:25.661 --> 00:01:30.165
The misrepresentation and misuse
and manipulation of religious scripture

00:01:30.165 --> 00:01:33.694
has influenced our social
and cultural norms,

00:01:33.694 --> 00:01:36.620
our laws, our daily lives,

00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:40.474
to a point where we sometimes
don't recognize it.

00:01:40.804 --> 00:01:45.490
My parents moved from Libya,
North Africa, to Canada

00:01:45.490 --> 00:01:47.254
in the early 1980s,

00:01:47.254 --> 00:01:51.100
and I am the middle child of 11 children.

00:01:51.100 --> 00:01:52.431
Yes, 11.

00:01:53.431 --> 00:01:55.589
But growing up, I saw my parents,

00:01:55.589 --> 00:01:59.165
both religiously devout
and spiritual people,

00:01:59.165 --> 00:02:01.905
pray and praise God for their blessings,